<HEAD>Former Finance Minister Dead at 72</HEAD>
<DATELINE>KUALA LUMPUR, Malaysia (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Tan Siew Sin, former finance
minister and head of a multinational company based here, died
Friday of a heart attack at age 72.
